de.ityx.mediatrix.data

Class Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.ErpsData
      • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.Profile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IErpsData, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Operator

    public class Profile
extends ErpsData
    Each operator has responsibilities in one or many subprojects. They may be assigned manually or per profile(predefined settings of the permissions and responsibilities). The profiles can be assigned or applied to the operators.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
